metadata.name: Crypto Monks #0001
metadata.description:
This is the first installment of crypto monks. Value #0001. (the very og)

Each monk is hand made. I click the color of every single pixel. No randomization besides what my brain decides is good. Different background colors equate to different tiers. I am going to create one to two thousand of these over time. Depends on the demands of the people, as I will collectively take everyone's perspective and process a decision. I really hope you enjoy this collection, and would love if you joined the discord and made any suggestions. I am always open to feedback.

Join our discord or check us out on twitter.

thank you for your time.
